Partly cloudy- warm- little lake traffice

Clear 75 degree day.  Minimal traffic on lake.  One single loon was spotted.  One nest with two eggs (loon) spotted.  This nest has been abandoned for two weeks.  Bonnie Syzck and Ken Kroiss helped with collection and measurements.
Sunny clear day.  Lake is calm with little boat traffic.  Ken Kroiss- Joe Burger- and Bonnie Szydel assisted.
